  "Likely equipped with advanced optics."\
  "Capable of rapid maneuver and coordinated counterattacks"\
  ""\
  "Most Likely Course of Action (MLCOA):"\
  "Establish defensive positions around high-value assets"\
  "Conduct ambushes along key terrain and avenues of approach"\
  ""\
  "Most Dangerous Course of Action (MDCOA):"\
  "Rapid coordinated assault on REDFOR insertion or extraction zones"\
