 {
  coords 10852.276 1.344 1938.66
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "INFOR (ION) is to protect the general at all costs. Once the spawn-in time is complete, ION forces can move anywhere on the island to prevent the General's capture."\
  ""\
  "DO NOT TAKE THE GENERAL TO THE DOCK OR HELICOPTER PAD. We suspect that's where enemy forces have inserted to capture the general."\
  ""\
  "DO NOT, UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES, GIVE THE GENERAL A GUN. He has accidently TK'ed three people on his way here... he's a menace."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_ION"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 {
  coords 10851.996 1.345 1939.907
  m_sTitle "Execution"
  m_sTextData "Commander's Intent"\
  ""\
  "<h2>Considerations</h2>"\
  "Secure the general's primary position."\
  "Have a secondary and possible tertiary (third) fallback position."\
  "If the general is captured, use your vehicles to outpace the enemy."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_ION"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 {
